    <h1>GridPrint Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: October 2025</p>
    <p>GridPrint is a Chrome extension that allows users to create printable grids of images, supporting A4 and A3 page sizes with PDF export. All processing is done locally on your device.</p>
    <p><strong>Data Collection and Usage:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>GridPrint does not collect, store, or transmit any user data.</li>
      <li>Images uploaded by users are processed locally and are not sent to any servers or third parties.</li>
      <li>No personal information is gathered, and no analytics or tracking are used.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Contact:</strong> For questions or feedback, reach out to <a href="mailto:mrjamesdorey@gmail.com">mrjamesdorey@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </main>
